*&      Module  USER_COMMAND_0100  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
module user_command_0100 input.
** to react on key-press-events:
*  call method cl_gui_cfw=>dispatch.
  case ok_code.
    when 'EXIT'.
      leave to screen 0.
    when 'LEFT'.
      perform handle_left.
    when 'RIGHT'.
      perform handle_right.
    when others.
  endcase.
  clear ok_code.
  game->refresh( ).
endmodule.
